{
  "chapter": 171,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙以万瑞光身份率庄夫人一行抵达楚都寿春，在码头等候时，春申君黄歇亲来迎接。庄夫人哭诉求助，黄歇虽表面客气，但对复国之事并不热心。庄夫人要求返回滇王府，才知府第已被左令尹李闯文强占多年。项少龙决意先礼后兵，派人通知李闯文后率众直奔滇王府。在府前与李闯文对峙，项少龙假意退让诱其出言不逊，待李闯文下令动手后，众铁卫取出藏于车底的重木棍，以迅雷之势击溃二百多名府中武士。项少龙如出柙之虎冲入大堂，当众打断李闯文小腿，下令将所有霸占者扔出街外，为庄家夺回府第立威。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "庄夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那胖子就是春申君黄歇。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "比我上次见他之时，又胖了一点。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "庄夫人",
      "listener": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "text": "君上要为妾身、犬子作主啊！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黄歇",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_fu_ren",
      "text": "万王妃请勿悲伤，一切回府后再从长计议。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黄歇",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "久仰万先生之名，果是一表人才，本君好生欢喜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "万瑞光",
      "listener": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "text": "君上威名震天下，该是瑞光感到荣幸才对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黄歇",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_fu_ren",
      "text": "王妃不若先到敝府歇息，其他一切慢慢商议。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_kong",
      "speaker_name": "庄孔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那人就是方卓！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "庄夫人",
      "listener": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "text": "不用打扰君上了，妾身只想返回滇王府去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黄歇",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_fu_ren",
      "text": "这事也待回到敝府后再说好吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "庄夫人",
      "listener": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "text": "请问君上，这事有什么问题呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黄歇",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_fu_ren",
      "text": "自滇国乱起后，王妃和小公子避往秦地，滇王府的婢仆四散潜逃，丢空了多年，最近左令尹李闯文见了颇为心喜，强行搬进滇王府去，本君虽曾多次与他交涉，可是他仗着先王的默许，一概不理睬，本君也极为不满。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "庄夫人",
      "listener": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "text": "天理何在，君上须为妾身讨回公道。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黄歇",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_fu_ren",
      "text": "早晚本君会使这小子受到教训，不过现在形势微妙，不宜轻举妄动。王妃舟车劳顿，不若先回敝府休息吧！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "万瑞光",
      "listener": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "text": "君上好意心领了，今趟我们来寿春，正是要讨回公道，若胆怯怕事，何能完成复国大业？君上请先回府，我们自有主意。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黄歇",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "李闯文这一莽撞行为，很多人看不顺眼，就是李族中人亦有微言，诸侯国派驻此处的使臣更曾联名上书抗议，只是给先王一直拖着，万将军若要把王府夺回，无人敢说半句话，只不过李闯文府内家将中高手如云，起了冲突时后果难料，万将军还请三思，而本君更不便直接参与。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "万瑞光",
      "listener": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "text": "'自反而缩，虽千万人，吾往矣'！君上可否先遣人通知李闯文，说我们要立即收回滇王府，来个先礼后兵。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黄歇",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "万先生果是真豪杰，我黄歇服了，人来！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "方卓",
      "listener": "char_chun_shen_jun",
      "text": "这事由小人去办吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "李闯文手下",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "来人止步，何故乱闯我府？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "万瑞光",
      "listener": "char_li_chuang_wen",
      "text": "何人霸占我滇王的府第，给我万瑞光报上名来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chuang_wen",
      "speaker_name": "李闯文",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "真是好笑，滇王因不擅治国，早于五年前被当地民众杀死，还哪里找个滇王出来？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "万瑞光",
      "listener": "char_li_chuang_wen",
      "text": "好胆，我家储君在此，谁敢说滇王不在，你这强占滇王府的狂徒，可敢和我到大王座前理论，查看有关国玺、文书、令符，以证我储君方是滇国之主。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chuang_wen",
      "speaker_name": "李闯文",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你才是狂妄之徒，谁知你是否乱臣贼子，弄些假证物来招摇撞骗，快给我滚出大门去，否则我就把你们的狗腿子全敲断。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "万瑞光",
      "listener": "char_li_chuang_wen",
      "text": "你既不相信，我这就去面谒太后、大王，请求评个公道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chuang_wen",
      "speaker_name": "李闯文",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "走得这么容易吗？待我把你们绑往见太后吧！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chuang_wen",
      "speaker_name": "李闯文",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "动手！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_chuang_wen",
      "text": "原来你不但是狂徒，还是胆怯之徒！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chuang_wen",
      "speaker_name": "李闯文",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我乃大楚令尹，你若敢动我半根毫毛……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "将所有霸占我滇王府的狂贼，全给我扔出街外。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 171,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    }
  ],
